    <h1>Content Curation</h1>
    <p class="description">Finding, filtering, and sharing relevant third-party content — with your perspective added. The <strong>60/40 rule</strong> keeps most publishing calendars sustainable without burning creative resources.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
