            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">What is the 60/40 rule of content curation?</span><span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span></button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>The 60/40 rule is a publishing mix — roughly 60% original content and 40% curated content. It keeps a steady cadence without draining creative resources.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">Does content curation help SEO?</span><span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span></button>
